---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About THHT (thôt)"
  description="A bit about Thinking Hard / Hardly Thinking and the person behind it."
  pubDate={new Date()}
>
  <p>
    This is <strong>Thinking Hard / Hardly Thinking</strong> — a blog that exists somewhere between
    a public notebook and a thinking-out-loud session. Not every post will be polished.
    Not every argument will be airtight. But everything here is written because it felt
    worth saying out loud.
  </p>

  <p>
    The title is a joke that stopped being funny halfway through, which felt appropriate
    for a blog about ideas. Sometimes I'm thinking very hard. Sometimes I'm hardly thinking.
    Usually I'm somewhere in between, trying to figure out which one it is.
  </p>

  <p>
    Topics might include whatever I'm reading, researching, or confused about — and
    I expect that range to wander. If something regularly pulls me in, it will
    probably end up here.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <p>
    If you found something worth responding to, I'd genuinely like to hear from you.
    You can reach me at <a href="mailto:kartik0trivedi@gmail.com">kartik0trivedi@gmail.com</a>.
  </p>
</Layout>
